crashed into a moving car killing the cycles 21yearold driver 
police said police refused to say whether he was hit by the bullet 
wary police in riot gear kept automatic rifles poised 
occasionally dropping the barrel toward any rapid movement 
on the corner was a group of about 15 young black men angry 
nervous watching every police move 
the 43yearold mrs kennedy just over 5 feet tall in her pumps 
and wearing a bright red pants and top walked over 
what caused this to happen she asked 
