to grow 
a young shirtless teenager stepped forward 
the blacks have been here since i dont know when he said 
but 10000 cubans a year they get jobs just like that and now 
the nicaraguans 
miami officials have been providing shelter at a stadium for 
about 250 nicaraguans seeking political asylum 
a stone clattered to the pavement and several police rifles 
leveled at the crowd 
dont you murder him came a cry from another teen were 
coming to your homes if theres another murder 
as the anger grew police quietly urged mrs kennedy into a 
waiting car 
during the ride through the streets of overtown with two officers 
and a reporter mrs kennedy got the scare of the night when her car 
approached a group of heavily armed policeman 
