follow within a few weeks 
gooch told reporters the current schedule for 1989 calls for 
seven delta 2s two commercial delta 2s and one delta 1 two titan 
4s two smaller titan 34ds and two commercial titan 3s two 
commercial atlascentaurs and one with a navy communications 
satellite and six to eight submarine test launches of the navys 
