1983 when there were 60 there were 26 in 1987 
but launch slippages and a shortage of manpower could hold down 
the total gooch said with luck we could support that rate but 
if we can get 70 percent up we will have earned our pay 
the air force decided to build the delta 2 and to greatly 
increase its titan 4 order following the explosion of space shuttle 
