personal responsibility for a situation in which the german people 
and the world public have long been decieved that germanamerican 
relations have been seriously hampered and that west germany has 
been exposed to worldwide suspicion of calling publicly for a ban on 
chemical weapons while secretly fostering their production 
petra kelly leader of the greens partys parliamentary 
delegation demanded that kohl resign over the governments 
mishandling of the issue 
