last year 17753 students nationwide worked during the summer 
months for various usda agencies and officials said they expect 
about that many this year the 563 jobs reserved for the black 
schools would represent about 3 percent of the total 
agriculture is more than crop and livestock production myers 
said animal and plant sciences economics forestry marketing 
and computer technology are just some of the varied career fields in 
agriculture today 
