the numbers were essentially in line with expectations 
lupatkin said of tuesdays report 
regarding the announcement of the price cut lupatkin said the 
company could be repositioning existing products in anticipation 
of a new product introduction 
i also think the price decline reflects the general slowing of 
overall industry growth the analyst added 
the company pointed to its commitment to new products in 
tuesdays announcement 
